001package doctorwhoapp.backend.data.entities;
002
003import jakarta.persistence.Column;
004import jakarta.persistence.Entity;
005import jakarta.persistence.FetchType;
006import jakarta.persistence.OneToOne;
007
008@Entity(name = "Doctor")
009public class DoctorEntity extends PersonEntity {
010    private int incarnationNumber;
011
012    @Column(nullable = false)
013    private String incarnationName;
014
015    private String slogan;
016
017    @OneToOne(fetch = FetchType.LAZY)
018    private DoctorEntity predecessor;
019
020    @OneToOne(fetch = FetchType.LAZY)
021    private DoctorEntity successor;
022
023    public int getIncarnationNumber() {
024        return incarnationNumber;
025    }
026
027    public void setIncarnationNumber(final int incarnationNumber) {
028        this.incarnationNumber = incarnationNumber;
029    }
030
031    public String getIncarnationName() {
032        return incarnationName;
033    }
034
035    public void setIncarnationName(final String incarnationName) {
036        this.incarnationName = incarnationName;
037    }
038
039    public String getSlogan() {
040        return slogan;
041    }
042
043    public void setSlogan(final String slogan) {
044        this.slogan = slogan;
045    }
046
047    public DoctorEntity getPredecessor() {
048        return predecessor;
049    }
050
051    public void setPredecessor(final DoctorEntity predecessor) {
052        this.predecessor = predecessor;
053    }
054
055    public DoctorEntity getSuccessor() {
056        return successor;
057    }
058
059    public void setSuccessor(final DoctorEntity successor) {
060        this.successor = successor;
061    }
062}
